        "authorId" : "25260d20-3dc9-4fc4-bf69-6aa8aae371ea",
        "body" : "Yes. Due to limitations on the windows side (mainly the fact that container networking is not supported), we couldn't use the infrastructure container for pods on windows. ",
        "createdAt" : "2016-12-15T16:05:09Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2017-02-16T19:52:46Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "25260d20-3dc9-4fc4-bf69-6aa8aae371ea",
